# Media Relations
Startups occasionally receive bad press. The nature of technology and innovation is such that even when your company is doing no harm, you can recieve pushback from the media. 
This problem is exaccerbated when your product is shit, your team are in it for the wrong reasons, and the whole thing is a huge mess. See:
